Zero point energy                ...      0.37917262 Eh     237.93 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.02253657 Eh      14.14 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
